            <title><![CDATA[Telenet Shooting Collection I + II physical bundle announced]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/03/telenet-shooting-collection-i-ii-physical-bundle-announced</link>
            <guid>1477099</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Pre-orders open on April 2.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> has announced <em><a title="Games > Telenet Shooting Collection I + II" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/telenet-shooting-collection-i-ii">Telenet Shooting Collection I + II</a></em>, a physical bundle that includes both <em><a title="Games > Telenet Shooting Collection [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/telenet-shooting-collection">Telenet Shooting Collection</a></em> and <em><a title="Games > Telenet Shooting Collection II [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/telenet-shooting-collection-ii">Telenet Shooting Collection II</a></em>, available in English. It will launch in Q2 2026. Pre-orders will open on April 2 in <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/telenet-shooting-collection-iii/13/70jbfj?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">standard</a> and <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/telenet-shooting-collection-iii-limited-edition/13/70jbf5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">limited editions</a>. (You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong><a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">GEMATSU</a>2025</strong>” coupon code.) <span id="more-1037171"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the new release, via Play-Asia:</p><blockquote><p><strong>■ About</strong></p><p>This exclusive bundle unites two beloved collections into one complete package, celebrating the legacy of classic <a title="Genres > Shoot 'Em Up [851 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/shoot-em-up">shoot ’em up</a> titles originally developed by Telenet Japan. For the first time, fans can enjoy both collections together in a physical Asia English version, fully compatible with <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> and Switch 2, and featuring English box art packaging.</p><p><strong>A Definitive Retro <a title="Genres > Shooter [4,404 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/shooter">Shooter</a> Collection</strong></p><p><em>Telenet Shooting Collection I + II</em> brings together eight iconic titles from the golden era of 16-bit gaming:</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>Telenet Shooting Collection I</em> includes:</p><ul><li><em>Granada</em> (1990, Genesis)</li><li><em>Avenger</em> (1990, PC Engine)</li><li><em>Gaiares</em> (1990, Genesis)</li><li><em>Psychic Storm</em> (1992, PC Engine)</li></ul><p><em>Telenet Shooting Collection II</em> includes:</p><ul><li><em>Kiaidan 00</em> (1992, PC Engine)</li><li><em><a title="Games > Final Zone [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/final-zone">Final Zone</a> II</em> (1990, PC Engine)</li><li><em>Browning</em> (1992, PC Engine)</li><li><em>Legion</em> (1990, PC Engine)</li></ul><p>High-speed mech combat meets classic horizontal and vertical shooters in a collection that showcases the definitive <a title="Genres > Action [3,445 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a> of a generation.</p><p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Play-Asia Exclusive Release</strong> – Available only via Play-Asia.</li><li><strong>Asia English Version</strong> – English cover and language support.</li><li><strong>Physical Release</strong> – A must-have for collectors and retro enthusiasts.</li><li><strong>Next-Gen Compatibility</strong> – Playable on Switch and Switch 2.</li></ul><p><strong>■ Play-Asia Exclusive: Two Editions Available</strong></p><p>To celebrate this collaboration, Play-Asia will produce two exclusive editions:</p><p><strong>Standard Edition</strong></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Telenet-Shooting-Collection-I-II_2026_03-30-26_007.jpg"></a></figure><ul><li>Physical copy of <em>Telenet Shooting Collection I + II</em></li></ul><p><strong>Limited Edition</strong></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Telenet-Shooting-Collection-I-II_2026_03-30-26_008.jpg"></a></figure><p>A premium collector’s set that includes:</p><ul><li>Physical copy of <em>Telenet Shooting Collection I + II</em></li><li>Exclusive mini case</li><li>PC Engine HuCard design USB stick card</li><li>Art book</li><li>Joy-Con sticker set</li><li>Character magnet</li><li>Numbered certificate of authenticity</li></ul></blockquote><p>View a new set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/telenet-shooting-collection-i-ii/march-30-2026/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Screenshots</span></h2><div id="carousel_1037178"><ul><li><span>❮</span></li><li><span>❯</span></li></ul></div></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/03/telenet-shooting-collection-i-ii-physical-bundle-announced]]></content:encoded>
            <dc:creator>invalid@example.com (ResetEra_Newsbot</dc:creator>
        </item>
