            <title><![CDATA[This Week’s Japanese Game Releases: Darwin’s Paradox!, Super Meat Boy 3D, more]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/03/this-weeks-japanese-game-releases-darwins-paradox-super-meat-boy-3d-more</link>
            <guid>1477042</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>GRIME II, RACCOIN: Coin Pusher Roguelike, Temtem: Swarm, etc.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Darwin's Paradox! [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/darwins-paradox">Darwin’s Paradox!</a></em> and <em><a title="Games > Super Meat Boy 3D [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/super-meat-boy-3d">Super Meat Boy 3D</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> are the highlights of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1037136"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > GRIME II [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/grime-ii">GRIME II</a></em> for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, and PC, <em><a title="Games > RACCOIN: Coin Pusher Roguelike [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/raccoin-coin-pusher-roguelike">RACCOIN: Coin Pusher Roguelike</a></em> for PC, and <em><a title="Games > Temtem: Swarm [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/temtem-swarm">Temtem: Swarm</a></em> for PlayStation 5 and PC, as well as the PlayStation 5 and <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> versions of&nbsp;<em><a title="Games > MotionRec [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/motionrec">MotionRec</a></em>, and the PlayStation 5 and Switch 2 versions of <em><a title="Games > South of Midnight [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/south-of-midnight">South of Midnight</a>.</em></p><p>In terms of physical releases, the only two titles releasing this week are game-key card versions of <a title="Companies > D3 Publisher [540 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/d3-publisher">D3 Publisher</a>‘s <em><a title="Games > POOL ROOM BILLIARD [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pool-room-billiard">POOL ROOM BILLIARD</a></em> and <em><a title="Games > SIMPLE Series for Nintendo Switch 2 Vol.1 THE Mahjong [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/simple-series-for-nintendo-switch-2-vol-1-the-mahjong">SIMPLE Series for Nintendo Switch 2 Vol.1 THE Mahjong</a></em>, which are already available digitally.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through <a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em>POOL ROOM BILLIARD</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/simple-series-for-nintendo-switch-2-vol2-the-billiards/13/70jhj7?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>) – Already available digitally worldwide. Game-key card.</li><li><em>SIMPLE Series for Nintendo Switch 2 Vol.1 THE Mahjong</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/simple-series-for-nintendo-switch-2-vol1-the-mahjong/13/70jhj5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch 2</a>) – Already available digitally. Game-key card.</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
        <h2><span>Digital-Only</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > ALL WILL FALL [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/all-will-fall">ALL WILL FALL</a></em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2706020/ALL_WILL_FALL/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Darwin’s Paradox!</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2989180/Darwins_Paradox/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/darwins-paradox-cb3517" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Fishbowl [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/fishbowl">Fishbowl</a></em> (PS5, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1638070/Fishbowl/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Goat Simulator 3 [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/goat-simulator-3">Goat Simulator 3</a></em> (Switch 2) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Go! Go! Mister Chickums [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/go-go-mister-chickums">Go! Go! Mister Chickums</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2436810/Go_Go_Mister_Chickums/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Go Home Annie: An SCP Game [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/go-home-annie-an-scp-game">Go Home Annie: An SCP Game</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>GRIME II</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2529790/GRIME_II/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Hozy [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/hozy">Hozy</a></em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3326230/Hozy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Juufuutei Raden's Guide for Pixel Museum [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/juufuutei-radens-guide-for-pixel-museum">Juufuutei Raden’s Guide for Pixel Museum</a></em> (Xbox Series, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, PC [<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p34wqxs0hv5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching w0rldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Logiart Grimoire [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/logiart-grimoire">Logiart Grimoire</a></em> (Xbox Series, Xbox One, PC [<a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/logiart-grimoire/9nfc67r34b2r" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Morkull Ascend to the Gods [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/morkull-ascend-to-the-gods">Morkull Ascend to the Gods</a></em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4108490/Morkull_Ascend_to_the_Gods/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>MotionRec</em> (PS5, Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>RACCOIN: Coin Pusher Roguelike</em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3784030/RACCOIN_Coin_Pusher_Roguelike/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>South of Midnight</em> (PS5, Switch 2) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Super Meat Boy 3D</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3288210/Super_Meat_Boy_3D/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/super-meat-boy-3d-c9341d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/super-meat-boy-3d/9nj67tqq51z0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Temtem: Swarm</em> (PS5, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2510960/Temtem_Swarm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li></ul><p>The PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and Switch titles listed above can be purchased through Japanese <a title="Platforms > PlayStation [49,687 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a> Network and <a title="Platforms > Nintendo [23,696 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> accounts using prepaid cards:</p><ul><li>PlayStation Store cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-1100-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/70dc0b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,100</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-3000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/%20-card-5000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk4?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-10000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10,000</a></li><li>Nintendo eShop cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2v?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1500-yen-japan-account/13/70cte9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,500</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-3000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2w?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-5000-yen-japan-account/13/705239?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-9000-yen-japan-account/13/70bkw5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">9,000</a></li></ul><p>Additionally, direct top-ups for <a title="Genres > Gacha" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/gacha">gacha games</a> are available <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/14/7133p?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>, including:</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/blue_protocol:_star_resonance/14/713bp?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blue Protocol: Star Resonance</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/genshin_impact/14/7133t?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Genshin Impact</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/honkai_star_rail/14/7133z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Honkai: Star Rail</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/love_and_deepspace/14/7134n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Love and Deepspace</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/marvel_rivals/14/7134t?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Marvel Rivals</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/love_and_deepspace/14/7134n?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Where Winds Meet</em></a></li><li><a href="https://www.play-asia.com/digital/direct_top_up/game_top_up/zenless_zone_zero/14/7134z?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Zenless Zone Zero</em></a></li></ul><h2><span>Demos, DLC, Updates, etc.</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > Inazuma Eleven: Victory Road [66 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/inazuma-eleven-victory-road">Inazuma Eleven: Victory Road</a></em> Four Free Major Update “The Rising Bond DLC” (PS5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PS4, Switch, PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > SHINOBI: Art of Vengeance [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/shinobi-art-of-vengeance">SHINOBI: Art of Vengeance</a></em> Downloadable Content “<a title="Companies > SEGA [2,738 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> Villains Stage” (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, PC)</li><li><em><a title="Games > TINY METAL 2 [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tiny-metal-2">TINY METAL 2</a></em> Closed Playtest (PC)</li></ul></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/03/this-weeks-japanese-game-releases-darwins-paradox-super-meat-boy-3d-more]]></content:encoded>
